	"system": {
		"description": "<p>At 1st level, you are more hardy and tenacious than the average scientist. Your scientist hit points change to the following:</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d8 per scientist level</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 8 + your Constitution modifier</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d8 (or 5) + your Constitution modifier per scientist level after 1st</p>\n<p>You also gain the following proficiencies and features:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You gain proficiency in medium armor and three martial weapons of your choice.</li>\n<li>You gain proficiency in Engineering and an expertise die on all Engineering checks.</li>\n<li>You gain an expertise die on checks using an engineer's toolbox.</li>\n<li>Expertise dice on Engineering checks and your chosen tool can be upgraded from d8 to d12, exceeding the usual limit on expertise dice.</li>\n</ul>",
